					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Those are the two things I REALLY wanted to avoid. I wanted to just make an article about wacky cartoon ducks and play it straight. Too many articles go the route of 1048ing something safe into something mermaid man would freak out about. I made loony-toons, not Peacock. These guys were made to fun and silly, not deadly and mysterious.</p> 
