						 <p>I believe this is one of my favourite SCPs which is strange because I've not been on this website for very long. I've been reading a lot though and this one is very good in my opinion. In the addendum, the attempted escape by the SCPs felt really cartoon-ish and not very foundation-y, but then I thought about it and remembered they all have a very strong connection with cartoons and slapstick humor. This is a very good indication that a lot of thought and planning went into this SCP. Very nice work.</p> 
				 	]]>
